{"tid":16370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"乜家陣啲健身中心sales可以咁無人性架咩","createTime":"2016-12-01T11:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T00:59:33.000Z","uid":39514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87ed62b71d74bccb7389fa58f6db719a259adbe3","tid":16370,"uid":39514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:53:29.000Z","msg":"咁啱行過有條友拉客<br />\n我話唔得閒佢就話老細睇住幫下手做個樣<br />\n之後又話差一個quota叫我幫幫手<br />\n我緊係彩佢都傻 佢又話唔駛簽啲咩淨係入去佢間野到比啲野我做個樣<br />\n我見佢咁誠懇又老老實實咁樣 又同我講閒計 我就話比二分鐘佢<br />\n入到去又問我叫咩名拎電話 我鳩up個名同電話出黎 諗諗下唔對路我就叫走人 佢又話比多一分鐘佢<br />\n最後另一條撚樣過左黎拎住張紙問三問四一睇就知做乜撚野  我二話不說走人<br />\n<br />\n利用人地良心做啲咁既野 祝你間野快啲執笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc14e886af977ba5efd2a47b2fe54e52bbd8ab29","tid":16370,"uid":26860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:56:24.000Z","msg":"老細睇住幫下手做個樣<br />\n之後又話差一個quota叫我幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n次次都用呢招，上次我畀咗個流嘅電話佢，佢仲要即刻話要打畀我，心諗真係 On 鳩鳩，即刻話電話無電唔會通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1480f2cfc6fa62f86e21bc67775d3f7b9801a072","tid":16370,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老細睇住幫下手做個樣<br />\n之後又話差一個quota叫我幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n次次都用呢招，上次我畀咗個流嘅電話佢，佢仲要即刻話要打畀我，心諗真係 On 鳩鳩，即刻話電話無電唔會通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下次留個警署電話俾佢話係屋企電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5450c9776cc84c299dae6c6026083df4d71ca08","tid":16370,"uid